item.title: CVE-2021-38347|2024-09-17T01:50:43.684Z -- custom%20website%20data -- custom%20website%20data
item.description: The Custom Website Data WordPress plugin is vulnerable to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting via the id parameter found in the ~/views/edit.php file which allows attackers to inject arbitrary web scripts, in versions up to and including 2.2.
